Wstaw przyimki z listy under, in, at, next to, near, in front of between, on
Emily is sitting 1) [...] her desk. The desk is 2) [...] the window. There is a lamp 3) [...] it.Emily's bed is 4) [...]
two small tables. There is a carpet 5) [...] the floor. Her cat is
6) [...] the bed. The wardrobe is 7) [...] her desk.
Emily's clothes are 8) [...] the wardrobe. There is an armchair
9) [...] the desk.
